<para id="fs-idm455966176"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objectives</emphasis>: Unit 8J Explain the causes and effects of continuing policy debates about the role of the federal government over time, Unit 9B Explain the causes and effects of continuing policy debates about the role of the federal government over time, Unit 9C Explain the causes and effects of the end of the Cold War and its legacy</para>
<para id="fs-idm217163152"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Developments</emphasis>: 8.3.III.C, 8.2.III.E, 8.2.III.F, 9.1.I.B, 9.3.I.A</para>
